==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: yī fēn gēngyún, yī fēn shōuhuò

===Etymology===
Literally: For each part sewn, one part is reaped.

===Proverb===
'''[[一]][[分]][[耕耘]]，[[一]][[分]][[收获]]'''

# You get out of it what you put into it.
# The more one works at something, the better the results.

===Alternate forms===
[[一分耕耘，一分收穫]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

